Thank you for the heads up on the Schaeffer parcel.  Just a reminder that if
we want to use that site for a laydown parcel it may be necessary to obtain
approval from the County to do so.  After Thursday night we can discuss the
proper method of confirming this with the County.  Please keep in mind that
while a we hope to obtain approval of a motion on Thursday night, formal
approval will not occur until next month's ZBA hearing when written findings
will be adopted.

 
