   Mark,  FYI  -  I plan to approach Mr. Schaeffer (the 28 acre tract
to the
   immediate west of the site) to option that tract as well once we get
done
   with the ZBA on Thursday (assuming it goes off without a hitch).

   We want to option that tract so it could be used as construction
laydown,
   and more importantly to control the parcel across from the plant
site.  The
   plan would be to buy the tract, but let him have rights to farming
it -
   once we're done using it for laydown.  This gives us a buffer tract
for
   sound mitigation etc. as well.





